title: Signup Wizard with Password Strength
prompt: Create a 3-step signup wizard using Stepper component. Step 1: TextInput for name and email. Step 2: PasswordInput with a Progress bar showing password strength. Step 3: Review section showing entered data with a submit Button. Include Back/Next buttons at the bottom. Use only Mantine core components, no icons.

title: Pricing Plans - Three Tier Comparison
prompt: Create a pricing plans comparison with 3 tiers using Cards: Basic ($9/mo), Pro ($29/mo with "Most Popular" Badge), and Enterprise ($99/mo). Each card should have: title, price, a list of 4-5 features with checkmarks (use Text components), and a Button at the bottom. Use SimpleGrid for the 3-column layout. Make the Pro card visually stand out with a different border color. Use only Mantine core components.

title: User Management Table with Pagination
prompt: Create a user management data table using Table component with 5 columns: Name, Email, Role (Badge), Status (Badge with color - green for active, red for inactive), and Actions (ActionIcon buttons). Show 8 rows of sample user data. Below the table, add a Pagination component. Use TableScrollContainer for responsive behavior. Include column headers with proper styling. Use only Mantine core components.

title: Event Scheduling Form
prompt: Create an event scheduling form with: a TextInput for event name, a Textarea for description, a Group with two TextInput components styled as date and time inputs (use type="date" and type="time" HTML attributes), a Select dropdown for event category (Meeting, Workshop, Conference, Social), and a Checkbox for "Send reminder". Include a Submit button. Use Card as container with proper spacing. Use only Mantine core components.

title: Professional Profile Page - LinkedIn Style
prompt: Create a professional profile page layout similar to LinkedIn. Use a 2-column Grid layout (main content 2/3, sidebar 1/3). Main column: (1) Profile header Card with BackgroundImage banner, Avatar overlapping the banner, user name Title, job title Text, location Text, connection count Badge, and Connect/Message buttons. (2) About Card with Text bio. (3) Experience Card with Timeline showing 3 job positions (company, role, dates). Sidebar column: (1) Profile stats Card showing views and connections counts. (2) Skills Card with 5 Badge items. Use only Mantine core components, no icons.
